{% extends 'adventure/graveyard.html.twig' %}
{% block title %}Adventure - {{app.request.attributes.get('_route')|title}} {% endblock %}


{% block roomtext %}

<p>
    The narrow path winds its way up the grassy hill, leading you to a small, timeworn cottage. Its thatched roof sags
    slightly with age, and the red door stands closedâ€”silent, yet inviting. Wind whispers through the nearby trees, as
